<BaseLayout
  title="Attribution & provenance — YGO × MTG"
  description="Fan-project, source, asset, and mana-symbol attribution for the YGO × MTG showcase."
>
  <article class="page-shell legal-copy">
    <h1>Attribution & provenance</h1><p>
      YGO × MTG is an independent, non-commercial fan design project. Yu-Gi-Oh!
      card names and characters belong to Konami and their respective rights
      holders. Magic: The Gathering terminology and mana symbols belong to
      Wizards of the Coast.
    </p><h2>Source-backed cards</h2><p>
      Published text comes from English folder-form Magic Set Editor projects in
      this repository. Card pages expose an allowlisted public data shape;
      editor notes, local paths, and unknown source fields are never public.
    </p><h2>Artwork and renders</h2><p>
      Canonical card renders are preserved in source projects. Public copies are
      regenerated without embedded source metadata. Publication remains subject
      to project asset approval and withdrawal records; withdrawing an asset
      removes it from future website output but cannot erase public Git history
      or existing clones.
    </p><h2>Historical snapshots</h2><p>
      Snapshots preserve selected public card data and render hashes against a
      complete section baseline. They document catalog history; they do not
      replace source projects.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
